# FraudIQ India — Technology Stack

**Document version 1.0 · June 2026 · Pilot-stage architecture**

This document records every major technology choice in the FraudIQ India platform and the rationale behind it. Where a choice differs from the US reference platform, the India-specific reason is noted. Versions reflect the target pilot baseline; they are pinned in infrastructure-as-code and updated through the standard change process.

